1. merge the web.config snippet into C:\ADFS\sts\web.config
   and adapt it to your situation
   (follow the guidelines in the XML comments)
2. copy the DLL into C:\ADFS\sts\bin
3. allow read access to DLL for entity "Network Service"
4. configure ADFS Trust Policy by selecting the tab called
   "Custom Transformation" and by pointing to the DLL
   and setting the classname to: "ClaimTransformer.ClaimTransformer"
